tip.text: Delicious variety of brekkie options with some great coffee too.
Ask for the spicy Ramen and go all the way to level 3 to test your mettle.
Breakfast bagels are a great option here. Although you'll probably fall in love with the kitschy ambience which is definitely a geek's paradise.
Very friendly service with a decent selection of single malts and whiskey cocktails.
Great outdoor spot for a light meal or a summer drink.
One of the many Japanese restaurants and karaoke joints that don the CBD. Touchpad menus and super fast service are impeccably impressive.
Scrumptious burgers with an absolute cracker of a beach view. A Manly must.
New cafe around the corner. Spacious with an eclectic seating arrangement and a section for bibliophiles.
Superb whiskey and cocktail haunt with the perfect ambient and live music. Simply aces!
Decent vegetarian snack options in the Surry Hills area. South Indian is surprisingly good despite their speciality being chat and street food.
